GNU Linux-libre, Free as in Freedo
GNU Linux-libre，像 Freedo 一样自由

Linux, the kernel developed and distributed by Linus Torvalds et al, contains non-Free Software, i.e., software that does not respect your essential freedoms, and it induces you to install additional non-Free Software that it doesn't contain. Even after allegedly moving all firmware to a separate project as of release 4.14, Linux so-called "sources" published by Mr Torvalds still contain non-Free firmware disguised as source code.
Linux 是由 Linus Torvalds 等人开发和分发的内核，包含非自由软件，即不尊重您的基本自由的软件，并且它会诱使您安装它不包含的其他非自由软件。即使据称从 4.14 版开始将所有固件移至单独的项目，Torvalds 先生发布的 Linux 所谓“源代码”仍然包含伪装成源代码的非自由固件。

Few people realize Linux is not free. The same thing happens to Stux, this cute penguin.
很少有人意识到 Linux 不是免费的。同样的事情也发生在这只可爱的企鹅 Stux 身上。

GNU Linux-libre is a project to maintain and publish 100% Free distributions of Linux, suitable for use in Free System Distributions, removing software that is included without source code, with obfuscated or obscured source code, under non-Free Software licenses, that do not permit you to change the software so that it does what you wish, and that induces or requires you to install additional pieces of non-Free Software.
GNU Linux-libre 是一个维护和发布 100% 免费 Linux 发行版的项目，适合在自由系统发行版中使用，删除了在非自由软件许可下没有源代码、带有混淆或模糊源代码的软件，不允许您更改软件以使其按照您的意愿运行，并导致或要求您安装其他非自由软件。

Our releases can be easily adopted by 100% Free GNU/Linux distros, as well as by their users, by distros that want to enable their users to choose freedom, and by users of those that don't.
我们的版本可以很容易地被 100% 免费的 GNU/Linux 发行版及其用户、希望让用户选择自由的发行版以及那些不自由的发行版的用户采用。

Although UTUTO-e was the first GNU/Linux distro to remove non-Free portions of Linux, GNU Linux-libre follows and improves on the practices established by gNewSense and BLAG.
尽管 UTUTO-e 是第一个删除 Linux 的非自由部分的 GNU/Linux 发行版，但 GNU Linux-libre 遵循并改进了 gNewSense 和 BLAG 建立的实践。

Free Software Foundation Latin America (FSFLA) joined the (then non-GNU) Linux-libre project as part of its campaign dubbed "¡Sé Libre!", to encourage and enable users to go beyond using some Free Software, and rather seek and choose freedom.
拉丁美洲自由软件基金会 (FSFLA) 加入了（当时非 GNU）Linux-libre 项目，作为其名为“¡Sé Libre!”的活动的一部分，旨在鼓励并帮助用户超越使用某些自由软件的范围，而是寻求和使用自由软件。选择自由。

Downloads 下载

  • releases: source tarballs tracking upstream releases, from which we removed blobs and code that induces users to install non-Free Software.
    版本：跟踪上游版本的源 tarball，我们从中删除了诱导用户安装非自由软件的 blob 和代码。
  • git repository <git://linux-libre.fsfla.org/releases.git> carries tagged releases, scripts, and logs, in a far more compact form than the above.
    git 存储库 包含标记的版本、脚本和日志，其形式比上面的形式要紧凑得多。
  • SIGNING-KEY: The GnuPG keys used to sign source tarballs, patches, Freed-ora packages, and the keys that sign other repositories. For each repository R, there's a corresponding SIGNING-KEY.R in the download tree.
    SIGNING-KEY：用于签署源 tarball、补丁、Freed-ora 包的 GnuPG 密钥以及签署其他存储库的密钥。对于每个存储库 R，下载树中都有一个相应的 SIGNING-KEY.R。
  • Freesh: .debs for various architectures of the latest sources available. Read more.
    Freesh：.debs，适用于各种架构的最新可用源。阅读更多。
  • RPM Freedom: .rpms for Fedora, CentOS, RHEL and its derivatives. Read more.
    RPM Freedom：适用于 Fedora、CentOS、RHEL 及其衍生产品的 .rpm。阅读更多。
  • libeRTy: .debs compiled with the PREEMPT_RT patch for realtime operation on 32- and 64-bit x86 CPUs. Read more.
    libeRTy：使用 PREEMPT_RT 补丁编译的 .debs，用于在 32 位和 64 位 x86 CPU 上进行实时操作。阅读更多。
  • freed-ora: .rpms packages tracking Fedora kernel builds. Read more.
    freed-ora：跟踪 Fedora 内核构建的 .rpms 软件包。阅读更多。
  • Mirrors: The repositories above are available from our network of mirrors too.
    镜像：上面的存储库也可以从我们的镜像网络中获得。
  • Other binaries: There are other distributions of GNU Linux-libre binaries from third parties. We maintain a list.
    其他二进制文件：还有来自第三方的 GNU Linux-libre 二进制文件的其他发行版。我们维护一个列表。

2023-03-12 - i915 deblobbing bug fix
2023-03-12 - i915 去斑点错误修复

Initializing the i915 driver when using certain Intel i915 GPU variants appears to freeze the system: there is an infinite loop of disarmed (unsatisfiable) blob loading attempts in 6.1.-gnu (up to 6.1.18-gnu) and 6.2.-gnu (up to 6.2.5-gnu). See this thread for a workaround (that bypasses the loop but disables GPU acceleration), to confirm whether your GPU is affected, and for a patch, that fixes the problem without disabling GPU acceleration. The fix is slated for inclusion in upcoming releases, presumably 6.1.19-gnu, 6.2.6-gnu, and 6.3-rc*-gnu.
使用某些 Intel i915 GPU 变体时初始化 i915 驱动程序似乎会冻结系统：在 6.1.-gnu（最高 6.1.18-gnu）和 6.2.-gnu（最高 6.2.5-gnu）。请参阅此线程以获取解决方法（绕过循环但禁用 GPU 加速），以确认您的 GPU 是否受到影响，以及修复问题而不禁用 GPU 加速的补丁。该修复计划包含在即将发布的版本中，大概是 6.1.19-gnu、6.2.6-gnu 和 6.3-rc*-gnu。

2023-03-01 - Free Software Supporter
2023-03-01 - 自由软件支持者

The FSF is thankful for fifteen years of maintenance work, which provides the community with a reliable (and reliably free!) version of the kernel Linux for the GNU operating system. Such work by the Linux-libre maintainers helps to power all of the freedom-respecting distros, and thereby helps those of us who aim to drive our hardware with fully free software.
FSF 感谢 15 年的维护工作，为社区提供了适用于 GNU 操作系统的可靠（而且可靠免费！）的 Linux 内核版本。 Linux-libre 维护者的此类工作有助于为所有尊重自由的发行版提供动力，从而帮助我们这些旨在使用完全自由的软件驱动硬件的人。
-- FSF -- 自由软件基金会

We thank the FSF for the server, continued support and for the kind mention.
我们感谢 FSF 提供的服务器、持续的支持以及善意的提及。

2022-12-17 - Freed-ora is history
2022-12-17 - 释放奥拉已成为历史

With the EOLing of Fedora 35, Freed-ora has become inactive, after almost 15 years building freed versions of Fedora's blob-ridden kernels. For Fedora users interested in software freedom, we now recommend RPMFreedom kernel builds. Thanks to the various supporters of this subproject over the years.
随着 Fedora 35 的停产，在构建 Fedora 充满斑点的内核的免费版本近 15 年后，Freed-ora 已经不再活跃。对于对软件自由感兴趣的 Fedora 用户，我们现在推荐 RPMFreedom 内核构建。感谢多年来本子项目的各个支持者。

2021-09-27 - Removing obsolete releases and repositories
2021-09-27 - 删除过时的版本和存储库

We celebrate the 38th anniversary of the GNU Project and of the Free Software movement by removing past releases found to contain nonfree software. Their cleaning-up scripts remain available from the git repository, and from releases/old/gen6.
我们通过删除包含非自由软件的过去版本来庆祝 GNU 项目和自由软件运动 38 周年。他们的清理脚本仍然可以从 git 存储库和releases/old/gen6 中获取。

We're also removing long-obsolete repositories that still contained builds of those and of even earlier releases. Instead of freed-ebian and planet, we recommend Freesh. Instead of rt, we recommend LibeRTy. A freeloong replacement might be added to Freesh if there's enough demand.
我们还将删除长期过时的存储库，这些存储库仍然包含这些版本甚至更早版本的构建。我们推荐 Freesh，而不是 freed-ebian 和 Planet。我们推荐 LibeRTy，而不是 rt。如果有足够的需求，Freeloong 的替代品可能会被添加到 Freesh 中。

Freed-ora repositories for recent Fedora releases remain available, but we're still looking for new maintainers for Freed-ora.
最近 Fedora 版本的 Freed-ora 存储库仍然可用，但我们仍在寻找 Freed-ora 的新维护者。

2015-01-28 - Deblob scripts now have signatures, branches and tags
2015-01-28 - Deblob 脚本现在具有签名、分支和标签

The deblob scripts are now signed, in past and future source releases. Scripts published as part of past source releases were verified against the history stored in the version control repository.
deblob 脚本现已在过去和未来的源版本中进行签名。作为过去源版本的一部分发布的脚本已根据版本控制存储库中存储的历史记录进行验证。

In order to make this easier, and to make it easier for users to select stable sets of deblob scripts that work together, we now have per-major-release branches holding the latest version (and past history) of deblobbing scripts for that release. The first release coming out after each change to such a branch also gets a tag, so that every one of our source releases can be easily mapped and compared to a tag.
为了使这一切变得更容易，并让用户更容易选择协同工作的稳定的 deblob 脚本集，我们现在有每个主要版本的分支，保存该版本的 deblob 脚本的最新版本（和过去的历史记录）。每次更改此类分支后发布的第一个版本也会获得一个标签，以便我们的每个源版本都可以轻松映射并与标签进行比较。

See also the README file and the branches and tags subdirs within the releases tree in our version control repository.
另请参阅自述文件以及版本控制存储库中发布树中的分支和标签子目录。

2012-03-19 - 3.3-gnu: “3.3 as in freedom.freedom”
2012-03-19 - 3.3-gnu：“3.3 与 Freedom.freedom 一样”

Linux-libre joins the GNU Project, becoming GNU Linux-libre. This release, 3.3-gnu, marks the transition, although upcoming stable releases based on earlier -libre releases may become -gnu releases as well. Deblobbing scripts now support .gz, .lz and .xz compressed inputs, in addition to .bz2 and uncompressed ones, and tarballs are now named linux-libre--gnu.tar. Few deblobbing changes were required for this release: deblobbing of drivers for arm imx, dib0700, it913x, em28xx-dvb, brcmfmac, iwl3945, iwl4965, and rtl8192e needed some adjusting, while wl12xx-sdio-test and snd-intel-sst are no longer present, and sigmadsp code moved about in the tree.
Linux-libre 加入 GNU 项目，成为 GNU Linux-libre。这个版本 3.3-gnu 标志着这一转变，尽管基于早期 -libre 版本的即将发布的稳定版本也可能成为 -gnu 版本。除了 .bz2 和未压缩的输入之外，Delobbbbing 脚本现在还支持 .gz、.lz 和 .xz 压缩输入，并且 tarball 现在命名为 linux-libre--gnu.tar。此版本几乎不需要进行去斑点更改：arm imx、dib0700、it913x、em28xx-dvb、brcmfmac、iwl3945、iwl4965 和 rtl8192e 的驱动程序去斑点需要进行一些调整，而 wl12xx-sdio-test 和 snd-intel-sst 则不需要存在时间更长，并且 sigmadsp 代码在树中移动。

2009-03-31 - gen2 - 2.6.28-libre2 and 2.6.29-libre released
2009-03-31 - gen2 - 2.6.28-libre2 和 2.6.29-libre 发布

The 2.6.28-libre2 release fixes a number of problems in 2.6.28-libre1: some compile errors caused by deblobbing, a few missed non-Free firmware names and references to non-Free firmware, and some shell scripting portability issues. 2.6.28.9-libre2 is also available.
2.6.28-libre2 版本修复了 2.6.28-libre1 中的许多问题：一些由 deblobbing 引起的编译错误、一些丢失的非自由固件名称和对非自由固件的引用，以及一些 shell 脚本可移植性问题。 2.6.28.9-libre2 也可用。

The 2.6.29-libre release uses the same deblobbing infrastructure as 2.6.28-libre2, but it's updated for 2.6.29, and adapted to deal with the pieces of non-Free firmware and drivers that require external non-Free firmware added to the upstream release.
2.6.29-libre 版本使用与 2.6.28-libre2 相同的去斑点基础设施，但它针对 2.6.29 进行了更新，并进行了调整以处理需要添加外部非自由固件的非自由固件和驱动程序。上游版本。

2009-03-21 - gen2 - 2.6.28-libre1 released at Libre Planet 2009
2009-03-21 - gen2 - 2.6.28-libre1 在 Libre Planet 2009 上发布

This is the first release completely suitable for Free System Distributions: not only does it remove non-Free Software (and brings back some data tables that used to be removed in earlier release), it also removes requests for and documentation that induced users to install and use non-Free Software.
这是第一个完全适合免费系统发行版的版本：它不仅删除了非自由软件（并恢复了一些在早期版本中删除的数据表），还删除了引导用户安装的请求和文档并使用非自由软件。

Get the slides and the audio of the launch speech at the Libre Planet 2009 web site.
在 Libre Planet 2009 网站上获取启动演讲的幻灯片和音频。

How it is done
它是如何完成的

The removal of non-Free bits from the kernel Linux is accomplished with the script deblob-main, that in turn uses deblob- and deblob-check.
从 Linux 内核中删除非自由位是通过脚本 deblob-main 完成的，该脚本又使用 deblob- 和 deblob-check。

deblob- is inspired in gNewSense's scripts, later customized for BLAG by Jeff Moe, and then further improved as part of the linux-libre project.
deblob- 受到 gNewSense 脚本的启发，后来由 Jeff Moe 为 BLAG 定制，然后作为 linux-libre 项目的一部分进一步改进。

deblob-check is a script that you can use to test whether a kernel source file, a patch or a tarball, contains any remaining or suspicious firmware blob.
deblob-check 是一个脚本，可用于测试内核源文件、补丁或 tarball 是否包含任何剩余或可疑的固件 blob。

SVN repository structure
SVN存储库结构

  • scripts/deblob-main: The main script to clean up a linux tarball.
    scripts/deblob-main：清理 Linux tarball 的主脚本。
  • scripts/deblob-check: A script that recognizes and optionally cleans up blobs.
    scripts/deblob-check：识别并选择性清理 blob 的脚本。
  • scripts/deblob-$ver: Scripts that clean up blobs from within exploded Linux source trees.
    scripts/deblob-$ver：从分解的 Linux 源代码树中清除 blob 的脚本。
  • scripts/README: More details on usage of these scripts.
    脚本/自述文件：有关这些脚本的使用的更多详细信息。
  • releases: Branches and tags of released scripts.
    releases：已发布脚本的分支和标签。
  • freed-ora: See freed-ora.
    freed-ora：参见 freed-ora。
  • freed-ebian: Scripts and diffs used to maintain freed-ebian packages.
    freed-ebian：用于维护 freed-ebian 软件包的脚本和差异。
  • lemote: Scripts and diffs used to maintain freeloong GNU Linux-libre binary packages for Lemote Yeeloong notebooks running gNewSense.
    lemote：用于维护运行 gNewSense 的 Lemote Yeeloong 笔记本的 freeloong GNU Linux-libre 二进制包的脚本和差异。

Other sources of binaries
其他二进制文件来源

  • Jason Self maintains both the Freesh apt repository with .debs of recent Linux-libre releases for 32- and 64-bit x86 and powerpc as well as the libeRTy apt repository which carries .debs compiled with the PREEMPT_RT patch for realtime operation on 32- and 64-bit x86 CPUs. Read more.
    Jason Self 维护 Freesh apt 存储库，其中包含最新 Linux-libre 版本的 .debs，适用于 32 位和 64 位 x86 和 powerpc，以及 libeRTy apt 存储库，该存储库携带使用 PREEMPT_RT 补丁编译的 .debs，以便在 32 位和 64 位 x86 和 powerpc 上进行实时操作。 64 位 x86 CPU。阅读更多。
  • Robert Musial has built DeCentOS RPMs.
    Robert Musial 构建了 DeCentOS RPM。
  • The GNU Guix System Distribution uses GNU Linux-libre as its kernel. Obviously
    GNU Guix System Distribution 使用 GNU Linux-libre 作为其内核。显然
  • BLAG ships our Freed-ora kernels. GdNewHat used to do that, too, before it merged with BLAG.
    BLAG 提供了我们的 Freed-ora 内核。 GdNewHat 在与 BLAG 合并之前也曾经这样做过。
  • gNewSense ships Linux-libre kernels. They used to be cleaned up with an older approach, but current releases use current deblobbing technology. For Lemote Yeeloong mipsel notebooks, see our repository.
    gNewSense 附带 Linux-libre 内核。它们曾经使用较旧的方法进行清理，但当前版本使用当前的去斑点技术。对于 Lemote Yeeloong mipsel 笔记本，请参阅我们的存储库。
  • Damián Fossi maintains Linux-libre binaries for gNewSense/MIPS (for Lemote Yeeloong laptops), and for Canaima GNU/Linux.
    Damián Fossi 维护 gNewSense/MIPS（用于 Lemote Yeeloong 笔记本电脑）和 Canaima GNU/Linux 的 Linux-libre 二进制文件。
  • Henry Jensen maintains the slack-n-free repository, with ConnochaetOS' GNU Linux-libre packages, so that they can be used on distros that cut non-Free Software too much slack.
    Henry Jensen 维护着 slack-n-free 存储库，其中包含 ConnochaetOS 的 GNU Linux-libre 软件包，这样它们就可以在那些对非自由软件过于宽松的发行版上使用。
  • FreeSlack also includes GNU Linux-libre packages in its installable images.
    FreeSlack 还在其可安装映像中包含 GNU Linux-libre 软件包。
  • VENENUX GNU/Linux switched to Linux-libre as of its 0.8-rc3 release.
    VENENUX GNU/Linux 从 0.8-rc3 版本起切换到 Linux-libre。
  • Trisquel ships 100% Free Linux kernels, based on Linux-libre from version 2.1 onwards.
    Trisquel 提供 100% 免费的 Linux 内核，基于 Linux-libre 从 2.1 版开始。
  • Drágora GNU/Linux has shipped Linux-libre in all of its releases.
    Drágora GNU/Linux 在其所有版本中都提供了 Linux-libre。
  • Kongoni has adopted Linux-libre as of the Nietszche release.
    Kongoni 从 Nietszche 版本开始就采用了 Linux-libre。
  • VegnuX NeonatoX GNU/Linux has shipped Linux-libre since the 0.48 release.
    自 0.48 版本以来，VegnuX NeonatoX GNU/Linux 已经提供了 Linux-libre。
  • Amagi is a gNewSense-based distro for Lemote Yeeloong laptops.
    Amagi 是一个基于 gNewSense 的 Lemote Yeeloong 笔记本电脑发行版。
  • Parábola GNU/Linux has Linux-libre binaries in its package repositories. If you use the distro on which Parábola is based, these packages could turn it into Freeda d'Arc.
    Parábola GNU/Linux 在其软件包存储库中具有 Linux-libre 二进制文件。如果您使用 Parábola 所基于的发行版，这些软件包可以将其变成 Freeda d'Arc。
  • ConnochaetOS is a light distro, also with Freeda d'Arc potential.
    ConnochaetOS 是一个轻量级发行版，也具有 Freeda d'Arc 的潜力。
  • RMS GNU/Linux-libre (RMS's Mostly Slax) shipped Linux-libre in a Live pen-drive light distro.
    RMS GNU/Linux-libre（RMS 的主要是 Slax）在 Live 笔式驱动器轻型发行版中提供了 Linux-libre。
  • Tlamaki GNU con Linux was based on Trisquel, but it rebased, becoming a FreedSUSE.
    Tlamaki GNU con Linux 基于 Trisquel，但它进行了重新设计，成为 FreedSUSE。
  • Musix GNU+Linux's adoption of Linux-libre is underway.
    Musix GNU+Linux 对 Linux-libre 的采用正在进行中。
  • Dyne:bolic is going to have Linux-libre in its next release.
    Dyne:bolic 将在其下一个版本中包含 Linux-libre。
  • Heads, also from the fine Dyne folks, is a Tor-enabled liveCD that uses a security-hardened kernel cleaned up with our deblobbing scripts.
    Heads 也来自优秀的 Dyne 人员，是一个支持 Tor 的 liveCD，它使用经过我们的 deblobbing 脚本清理的安全强化内核。
  • Genfree ebuild scripts are available too, thanks to Nick White.
    感谢 Nick White，Genfree ebuild 脚本也可用。
  • There are binary packages for Arch [GNU/]Linux.
    Arch [GNU/]Linux 有二进制包。
  • The “Linux Libre Packages” team maintains binary packages of GNU Linux-libre for free human beings.
    “Linux Libre Packages”团队为自由人类维护 GNU Linux-libre 的二进制包。
  • Aurélien Desbrières used to build Linux-libre/planet .debs for x86 out of Linux-libre tarballs, for general use. Read more.
    Aurélien Desbrières 曾经使用 Linux-libre tarball 为 x86 构建 Linux-libre/planet .debs，以供一般用途。阅读更多。
  • Ali Gündüz used to do that, too.
    Ali Gündüz 也曾经这样做过。
  • Juan Jacobo Nájera used to maintain the rt apt repository with .debs with real-time support. Read more.
    Juan Jacobo Nájera 过去使用 .debs 来维护 rt apt 存储库并提供实时支持。阅读更多。
  • James Turner used to build binary .debs of recent Linux-libre releases for Lemote Yeeloong (mipsel) netbooks.
    James Turner 曾经为 Lemote Yeeloong (mipsel) 上网本构建最新 Linux-libre 版本的二进制 .debs。
  • Robert Millan used to build Freed-ebian packages.
    Robert Millan 曾经构建 Freed-ebian 软件包。
  • If you roll out your own generally-available Linux-libre-based binaries, let us know.
    如果您推出自己的通用的基于 Linux-libre 的二进制文件，请告诉我们。

Artwork 艺术品

The hanging penguin picture was taken by Lewis Laë in November, 2007, and he was kind enough to grant us permission to use it as a logo, in private e-mail. Merci beaucoup, lew!
悬挂的企鹅照片是 Lewis Laë 于 2007 年 11 月拍摄的，他很友善地允许我们在私人电子邮件中使用它作为徽标。谢谢你，卢！

Anyhow, the picture didn't make for a very good logo. The penguin is cute and clean indeed, but he's still a prisoner. That's why we call him Stux.
无论如何，这张图片并不是一个很好的标志。企鹅确实可爱又干净，但他仍然是一个囚犯。这就是为什么我们称他为 Stux。

Burnaron drew Freetz (thanks!), the penguin above, shown getting out of the shower holding a brush and a towel. He posted a vectorial version too (the image is a link to it).
伯纳隆画了弗里茨（谢谢！），上面的企鹅，拿着刷子和毛巾走出淋浴间。他也发布了矢量版本（该图像是其链接）。

Rubén Rodrígues Pérez gave, erhm, birth to Freetz's younger brother, Freedo, our official logo. The name was suggested by Jeff Moe. Fernando suggested a grey version for printing in fewer colors. The final touches to Freedo were given by Islene Calciolari Garcia and Alexandre Oliva.
鲁本·罗德里格斯·佩雷斯 (Rubén Rodrígues Pérez) 生下了弗里茨的弟弟弗里多 (Freedo)，也就是我们的官方徽标。这个名字是由 Jeff Moe 建议的。费尔南多建议使用灰色版本，以较少的颜色进行打印。弗里多的最后润色由 Islene Calciolari Garcia 和 Alexandre Oliva 完成。

Alexandre Oliva combined Freedo with GNU, creating the image at the top of the page. Binaries published by the Linux-libre project are going to be configured to display this logo at boot up. If you want to use it too, look for patches named 100gnu+freedo.patch, in directories named after Linux-libre builds within SVN repository. A few kernels used an older variant:
Alexandre Oliva 将 Freedo 与 GNU 结合起来，在页面顶部创建了图像。 Linux-libre 项目发布的二进制文件将被配置为在启动时显示此徽标。如果您也想使用它，请在 SVN 存储库中以 Linux-libre 构建命名的目录中查找名为 100gnu+freedo.patch 的补丁。一些内核使用了旧版本：

Guillaume Pasquet drew Lux, the holy free penguin (thanks!), based on Larry Ewing's original tux; both must be credited for this art work.
纪尧姆·帕斯奎特 (Guillaume Pasquet) 根据拉里·尤因 (Larry Ewing) 原来的礼服绘制了拉克斯 (Lux)，这只神圣的自由企鹅（谢谢！）；两者都必须归功于这件艺术作品。

Alexandre Oliva put together the levitating gnu, and Lux, being levitated out of the cage. This picture and its vectorial corresponding sources are licensed under the same terms as the levitating gnu: GPLv3+ or GFDL1.1 without invariant sections, front or back cover texts.
亚历山大·奥利瓦（Alexandre Oliva）将悬浮牛羚和拉克丝组装在一起，将其从笼子中悬浮出来。该图片及其矢量对应源的许可条款与悬浮 gnu 相同：GPLv3+ 或 GFDL1.1，没有不变的部分、封面或封底文本。

Jason Self has drawn a collection of beautiful artwork with GNU and Freedo. Check it out!
Jason Self 与 GNU 和 Freedo 一起绘制了一系列精美的艺术作品。一探究竟！
